This code mixes AI Generative code with "real-people" code. [It works, but is not the finalized version.]
===========================================================================================================
Currently, multiple clients can connect to the server and send messages.
There are no issues with clients being disconnected, or messages not showing up on the server.
Clients can disconnect from the server by doing Ctrl + C.
